Class Reservation

java.lang.Object
Reservation
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Reservation extends Object implements Serializable
Represents a reservation, can be either a booking or walk‐in. There can only be 1 reservation under each contact number.
See Also:
Serialized Form

  • Field Summary

    Fields
    Modifier and Type
    Field
    Description
    int
    EXPIRYDURATION
    Fixed duration of 30 minutes from booking time, after which the reservation will expire
